                   with intention to defraud him, against the statute
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>A Second Count for uttering the said forged indorsement, knowing it to be forged, with the like intention.</p>
               <p>A third Count for forging the said indorsement, with intention to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t17840707-102-victim1036" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Jacobson
                  <interp inst="t17840707-102-victim1036" type="surname" value="Jacobson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-102-victim1036" type="given" value="William"></interp>
